  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/2d04fff53ce0f1e7c6870d24c47b7b7f.poster.avif?t=1747761589\" width=540 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/2d04fff53ce0f1e7c6870d24c47b7b7f.webm?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/2d04fff53ce0f1e7c6870d24c47b7b7f.mp4?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The one of a kind, fast paced, hardcore, arcade action, multiplayer, quick thinking, ele-ment absorbing, mental workout for everybody is back with a huge upgrade.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Ele-Mental offers a fast paced exciting  gameplay experience, perfect for local multiplayer or solo fun! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch Ele-Ments at the press of a button, dodge opposing Ele-Ments while absorbing those that match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/f10a6957728b194316fb17cc71e680ba.poster.avif?t=1747761589\" width=424 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/f10a6957728b194316fb17cc71e680ba.webm?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/f10a6957728b194316fb17cc71e680ba.mp4?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tighter Collisions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rebalanced unlockable costs and earned Coins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win medals for higher scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete missions fast for par.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Legend LeaderBoards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and save all the custom levels you could ever want.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom 8 stage arcade machines with your levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom 10 stage survival decathlons with your levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix 4 tunes by yourself now.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Audio.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Extra tunes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resolution and anti-alias selection. <br>     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/236f86472b69608e15fb7381b889eeaf.poster.avif?t=1747761589\" width=424 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/236f86472b69608e15fb7381b889eeaf.webm?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/236f86472b69608e15fb7381b889eeaf.mp4?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100 Progressively challenging missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 50 Survivals, from Casual to Ninja Pro. Doubled with Relentless mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 Survival Decathlons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 Arcade Machines, each with 8 rounds. (Can you perfect them all) (I Can't)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Creator Mode, create your own Missions and Survivals using all of the games mods and enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Little Ele-Venture, text based story adventure. Can you do the thing? (Normal and Hardcore)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Free Party Mode - Unlocks all Missions, Survival, Arcade and Creator in Competitive play, allowing for an untested number of players in a tournament.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/726f1462d0ec5c18c6dce52895549f27.poster.avif?t=1747761589\" width=544 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/726f1462d0ec5c18c6dce52895549f27.webm?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/726f1462d0ec5c18c6dce52895549f27.mp4?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1-4 player co-op on everything above.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Leaderboards for Survival, Missions, Arcade and Story modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pure co-op, for 2 or 4 players you are restricted charging Ele-Ments so you must rely on your team mates. (Available on everything)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pure Competition, 6 games with mods for competitive play outside of Free Party.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic Soundtrack evolves as you absorb.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > DJ Booth, 1-4 players each with a song from the game can remix all of the music. (This can get messy, Sync button recommended)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 14 Skins, 11 to unlock as you earn XP during play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ele-Medals. Like Achievements, but you get a little medal and some coins when you earn them. (Also Steam achievements)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stats. Ele-Ments absorbed, Enemy types absorbed, Games played, Mistakes made, coins earned, Fireworks purchased and More.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Personal stats, Name your self, choose a skin, rack up XP and Absorbs and see how long you've been playing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 129 Things to unlock.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/1d7f87038353751d4643533f94712367.poster.avif?t=1747761589\" width=540 height=62 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/1d7f87038353751d4643533f94712367.webm?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607820/extras/1d7f87038353751d4643533f94712367.mp4?t=1747761589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
